hopobject.body: How do you know each other? is voltaren gel good for sciatica The Irish low-cost airline has gone to great lengths to reduce the weight of its planes, cutting the size of its in-flight magazine, serving passengers less ice and even asking cabin crew to watch their figures. Last year Michael O’Leary, hoping to gain support for “standing room only” cabins, even suggested that seatbelts did “nothing” to prevent the death of passengers in a plane crash.
